  "texts": [
    "In the following we will specialize to small deflections, but it is worth emphasizing that the notion of the arrival-time surface t (θ) and its consequences have much wider applicability.",
    "Let us now turn Fig. 4 into equations, under the following simplifying assumptions.",
    "• All angles are taken to be small, in the sense of sin θ ≈ θ and cos θ ≈ 1 -1 2 θ 2.",
    "• Fig. 4 has the source far away from the lens.",
    "We now assume that the source is at infinity."
  ]
}